phrases: I am surprised you are knockin' back the booze during an emergency like this.
He is Gryder, a notorious drunk around these parts.
Nice that you are able to afford it.
Meanwhile, we are racing around in the name of justice.
Justice towards fighting against the returned Oracion Seis.
Justice towards protecting the citizens of Fiore.
Gryder, you got any sense of justice?
I do not want to hear it!
You think you can get away with pickin' a fight with Fiore soldiers?!
You are still using that name?
I need to speak with you.
There was a time when even you...
There is no need for you to fixate on justice.
Right now, I need your strength.
That is why I am here.
I will apologize if it will help.
I will take care of you later, Octopus Man!
You must be really confident to look away!
What the hell are you doing?!
We need to beat him with teamwork!
Wing Slash of the Fire Dragon!
Do you mean to cook and eat me-ebi?!
I want to cut that hair-ebi!
It looks like they just do not get along.
The combos should have good chemistry and their destinations should be on target.
Who goes mountain climbing in heels?
Well, after all, I am a fairy...
I told you I am in pain here!
You should worry about me at least a little!
You make a fuss just over that?
You should stop whining and focus on moving ahead.
Acting like she is the leader...
What a pain in the ass.
I would not be too sure of that...
I do not think I am...
Up against my Slot Magic, you are less than worms!
I think I will bombard you with dizzying changes!
We will not accomplish anything like this!
Are not nothing to think about!
There is only one thing to do!
Now this is my moment to shine-ebi!
Nobody asked you to do this!
Never mind teamwork, at this rate...
Like they say, each to their own taste, right?
Yeah, but I have got fish, you have Darjeeling tea...
It is delicious when you sink your teeth into it, skin and all.
Is that how you are supposed to eat it?
The sour taste spreads through my mouth, along with a subtle sweetness,
and the sensation of the skin!
As for me, I like this...
You are all silly little brats!
Gate of the Water Bearer, I open thee!
And you summoned me again from muddy water...
Do something about that machine monster!
Why do you always summon me when I am on a date?
I will take care of this punk nice and quick!
I am going to hit him first!
Actually, you are going to turn right around!
Both of you, shut the hell up!
They are not working together at all!
Say, Nico, I wonder how many more years this tree will live...
I was looking at this tree.
The situation we are in right now...
And how little time we have left, too.
Maybe this tree will remember us... is what I was thinking.
Word is that Fabrizio was found and taken away.
Maybe it is my turn next...
If you are scared, you can escape, Nico.
Is it that disagreeable to be paired up with me?
If you do not like it, you are free to run to that naked bastard.
I do not dislike you, Gajeel-kun.
Juvia and Grey-sama, drinking tea in a fancy open cafe...
Juvia wishes a tranquil day like this would last forever...
They have got that inside the shop, so get it from there!
The shop does not get much sunlight inside, so the iron is probably all rusty!
It is better to be out here!
Do not get in Juvia's way.
We are just going to drink together is all.
Juvia told you... do not get in my way!
That is what it is like...
But it is a pain in the ass...
That is the kind of woman Juvia is.
We will almost be at our destination once we make it past this mountain pass.
I guess the weather in the mountains changes quickly...
It is that Grim Reaper guy!
He is like a walking freakish weather system.
I take it that he used to be Erigor-san of Eisenwald.
You have got a lousy memory.
But I do know what the weather is going to be like next...
A blast of wind from above!
Along with occasional tornadoes from the side!
Do not underestimate Fairy Tail wizards!
We do not got time for that!
It is not coming to me...
But I know what the next weather pattern will be...
A storm from right in front of you!
What kind of soul does that girl have?!
I have already moved the souls to other dolls!
Hey, it is cowardly to fly out of the way!
By the way, who are you two?
He is already forgotten about us.
Wing Slash of the Sky Dragon!
You challenge me, master of weather phenomena, with wind magic?
Be careful of flying objects due to strong wind!
The Infinity Clock was completed and stolen by Oracion Seis.
So what are you people after now?
the situation is becoming more complicated than first anticipated, Nii-san.
So much that my calculations cannot keep up.
You want to help us, do not you?
After all, you are a fellow Exceed!
it is likely the humans will find themselves powerless to do anything.
I thought Zentopia's teachings were everything to you.
Doctrine is important too, but this is no time to be particular.
Sorry, but as Happy only ever has fish on the mind,
and Nii-san is just a musclehead, you two would not be able to comprehend it.
Did you come here to start another fight?!
Did you sense anything with your power of precognition?
I saw various unclear images, but they made me feel uneasy...
Images of the Key of the Starry Heavens?
I think it was a warning.
You were not meant to collect the pieces of the clock.
It seems the device was originally the property of Zentopia.
And now, we are being given an unfathomable mission.
Do you want to know the future, Sammy?
What is most ominous of all
is the possibility that Zentopia's doctrine is being misused.
We did not get here in time?
I totally... do not get it...
His Holiness gave us this mission, remember?
Why do you keep griping about it?
Are you one of Zentopia's, asshole?
Why did we... have to do that... to a priest?
His Holiness's words are the Archbishop's words.
In other words, it is doctrine.
If we are told to destroy something, it is Legion's job to destroy it!
According to doctrine, never, ever doubt the faith!
I do not like you, asshole!
It seems you both have extremely high levels of magic in your bodies.
What the hell is this thing?!
Juvia does not know this magic...
He swells up the magic power in a person's body instantaneously and makes it explode.
As long as you have magic power in your body,
I can keep you two dancing to my tune.
Why did you release someone like this?
We do not allow outsiders to enter.
When it comes to seducing a woman, the best way is a straight pitch.
What is it that you are proud of?
There is only one thing to do.
If you lay a hand on me, I will tell Cana!
It will be a mix of truth and lies, with 85 lies!
Do not take advantage of the situation to touch my privates!
It turned out this way after all...
All the hair on my body is standing on end!
You mean to say these people are creeping you out, right?
Do not try and mob us!
Jeez, what a pain in the ass!
A doll made from earth and wood?
It does not seem like Molding Magic...
What are those Zentopia clowns thinking?
Or more like, what are they hiding?
Maybe it is something even worse than the Master feared.
It looks like you were right on the money, Macao.
Has not Oracion Seis gotten a lot stronger than the last time we fought them?
Maybe it is because they cannot afford to lose for some reason...
But we cannot afford to lose either!
We are going to wipe the floor with them
and keep that chaos whatever from happenin'!
Natsu, that is a pretty important key phrase.
Winning is more important than words!
Well, yeah, but that is a blunt conclusion.
It is better to keep it simple with stuff like this.
